metadata.name: AlienGenesys #1
metadata.description: Alien Genesys is an art experiment. It is deranged and beautifully mesmerizing alien art, created by our AI, Virgil. It is a celebration of the recent advancements in AI and a commitment towards the future. Owning one of 333 genesys tokens will allow you to join our lab where you can create dope AI art and get premium access to many more future projects.
